library(tidyverse)

tmed.ts=ts(test$prom,start = 1981,frequency = 12)
arima_tmed<-auto.arima(tmed.ts)

forecast_PCP<-forecast(arima_PCP,level = c(95), h = 60)

pred_tmed_C4=autoplot(forecast_tmed)+xlab("Año")+ylab("Temperatura media [°C]")+ggtitle("Pronostico Temperatura media C4 - Cundinamarca",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2025")
